<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 03:22:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>小鹏汽车与大众汽车将在中国建设超快充电网络</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-volkswagen-build-ultra-fast-charging-network-china-2025-01-06/</link><description>中国小鹏汽车和大众汽车周一表示，双方已同意扩大合作伙伴关系，在中国超快速电动汽车充电网络方面进行合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 02:47:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-volkswagen-build-ultra-fast-charging-network-china-2025-01-06/</guid></item><item><title>吉利控股目标到2027年年销量突破500万辆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-holding-targets-over-5-million-units-annual-sales-by-2027-2025-01-06/</link><description>中国吉利控股集团 (GEELY.UL) 周日表示，其目标是到 2027 年年销量超过 500 万辆汽车，较 2023 年实现大幅增长，并希望通过加速整合旗下庞大品牌和提高效率来实现这一目标。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 01:58:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-holding-targets-over-5-million-units-annual-sales-by-2027-2025-01-06/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示，中国服务业活动创7个月新高，但美国贸易担忧削弱乐观情绪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-services-activity-hits-7-month-high-us-trade-fears-dent-optimism-caixin-2025-01-06/</link><description>周一的一项私营部门调查显示，在国内需求激增的推动下，12月份中国服务业活动以七个月以来最快的速度扩张，但海外订单下降，反映出经济面临的贸易风险不断加大。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 01:54:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-services-activity-hits-7-month-high-us-trade-fears-dent-optimism-caixin-2025-01-06/</guid></item><item><title>《华尔街日报》称，中国对美国电信设备的黑客攻击造成的公司数量比之前已知的还要多</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/chinese-hack-us-telecoms-compromised-more-firms-than-previously-known-wsj-says-2025-01-05/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》周六晚间援引知情人士的消息报道，中国黑客入侵的美国电信公司受到的损害比之前已知的还要多，其中包括 Charter Communications、Consolidated Communications (CCII.UL) 和 Windstream。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 14:35:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/chinese-hack-us-telecoms-compromised-more-firms-than-previously-known-wsj-says-2025-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国寻求加强西部地区的港口和航空枢纽</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-seeks-bolster-ports-aviation-hubs-western-regions-2025-01-05/</link><description>中国周日表示，将推出15条措施，通过建设港口、航空枢纽等物流基础设施来支持西部省份的发展。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 05:42:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-seeks-bolster-ports-aviation-hubs-western-regions-2025-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国市场大火造成8人死亡、15人受伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-market-blaze-kills-eight-15-hurt-2025-01-04/</link><description>据中央电视台周六报道，中国北部省份河北省的一个菜市场发生火灾，造成 8 人死亡、15 人受伤。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Jan 2025 09:05:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-market-blaze-kills-eight-15-hurt-2025-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>美国国家安全顾问访问印度讨论中国水坝问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-dams-be-discussed-during-india-visit-us-national-security-adviser-2025-01-03/</link><description>华盛顿及其西方盟友长期以来一直将印度视为中国在亚洲及其他地区影响力不断上升的对手。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 22:17:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-dams-be-discussed-during-india-visit-us-national-security-adviser-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>美国因涉嫌黑客攻击而制裁中国诚信科技</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-issues-cybersecurity-sanctions-against-chinas-integrity-technology-2025-01-03/</link><description>美国周五制裁了中国诚信科技集团，指责其是一个名为“亚麻台风”的多产黑客组织的幕后黑手。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 15:50:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-issues-cybersecurity-sanctions-against-chinas-integrity-technology-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>印度表示已向中国转达了对西藏水电站大坝的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-says-conveyed-concerns-china-over-hydropower-dam-tibet-2025-01-03/</link><description>中国官员表示，西藏水电项目不会对环境或下游水源产生重大影响。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 11:12:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-says-conveyed-concerns-china-over-hydropower-dam-tibet-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国为政府工作人员提供十年来首次大幅加薪以提振经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-gives-government-workers-first-big-pay-bump-decade-boost-economy-2025-01-03/</link><description>受此举影响的人士表示，中国各地数百万政府工作人员本周意外加薪，因为北京方面希望增加支出以支持经济放缓。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 07:19:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-gives-government-workers-first-big-pay-bump-decade-boost-economy-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国设立新的国家体育仲裁中心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-sets-up-new-national-sports-arbitration-centre-2025-01-03/</link><description>中国本周在首都北京开设了首个国家体育仲裁中心，为加强解决体育纠纷和保护运动员权利的法律框架迈出了关键一步。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 06:45:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-sets-up-new-national-sports-arbitration-centre-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>在商业航空经历了致命的一年之后，中国敦促进行安全评估</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-safety-assessments-after-deadly-year-commercial-aviation-2025-01-03/</link><description>继2018年以来全球商业航空死亡人数最多的一年之后，中国当局呼吁对行业风险进行评估，以发现从航线到跑道的任何“隐藏”运营风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 05:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-safety-assessments-after-deadly-year-commercial-aviation-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>2025年中国将大幅增加国债融资刺激经济增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-sharply-increase-funding-treasury-bonds-spur-growth-2025-2025-01-03/</link><description>一位国家规划官员周五表示，中国将在 2025 年大幅增加超长期国债资金，以刺激商业投资和消费刺激计划，同时北京将加大财政刺激力度，以重振步履蹒跚的经济。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 04:22:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-sharply-increase-funding-treasury-bonds-spur-growth-2025-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>海南免税消费大幅下滑，中国购物天堂陷入困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/trouble-chinas-shopping-paradise-hainan-duty-free-spending-falls-29-2025-01-03/</link><description>去年，由于经济疲软导致国内游客数量急剧下降，LVMH 和开云集团等全球奢侈品牌都在中国海南省开设了商店，免税支出下降了 29.3%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 02:41:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/trouble-chinas-shopping-paradise-hainan-duty-free-spending-falls-29-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行表示将适时降低银行存款准备金率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-might-cut-interest-rates-current-level-15-2025-ft-reports-2025-01-03/</link><description>根据周五发布的一份声明，中国央行表示将在上周举行的货币政策委员会季度会议上“适时”下调银行存款准备金率和利率。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 00:20:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-might-cut-interest-rates-current-level-15-2025-ft-reports-2025-01-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>